        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Filipino-style</strong> <strong>chicken adobo </strong>with the <strong>rice & tenderstem </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
